Carolina can do better and therefore request that the state
provide ample opportunity for public hearings on the issue of
redefining "Unit-6" as a minor polluter. I sincerely hope that
the State denies Duke Energy's request.

I urge you to promote energy efficiency and renewable energy
choices for North Carolina. Protect the health of North
Carolina's parks and people! Deny Duke Energy's Minor Source
application! Thank you for considering my views.



Sincerely,
